            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the veg is softening, grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>beef</strong> <strong>stock</strong> <strong>mix</strong> and <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>paste</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1694531491224-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1694531491224-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
