    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p><p>Combine your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> in a large bowl, add the <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>and toss together – this is your <strong>balsamic salad</strong></p>",
