    {
      "instruction": "<p>Leave the <strong>pork & beef lasagne tacos </strong>to stand for 5 min before serving (this helps the flavours to develop and makes it easier to serve!)</p><p>Serve the <strong>pork & beef lasagne tacos </strong>with the <strong>balsamic</strong> <strong>salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Discard the <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
